You saw the autopsy report.

42:28.800 --> 42:32.200
Wright was injected with a
lethal dose of potassium chloride.

42:32.200 --> 42:36.200
Obviously by this mercy killer.

42:36.680 --> 42:39.520
He was our only ally
with Magna-Fujiyama.

42:39.520 --> 42:42.040
Mark, you're being very quiet.

42:42.040 --> 42:44.680
You're usually so opinionated.

42:44.680 --> 42:48.000
I'm the one who contacted the HMO.

42:48.000 --> 42:51.720
This is all my fault.

42:51.720 --> 42:55.720
Mrs Huffnagel's death was a direct
