during the post-op period.

43:10.480 --> 43:14.480
In other words, I'm responsible
for Mrs Huffnagel's death.

43:19.480 --> 43:23.480
My father always said, "one life".

43:25.040 --> 43:29.040
One day in that life
is as precious as any other.

43:34.480 --> 43:38.480
